I"º<p>The <a href="http://www.raspberrypi.org" title="Raspberry Pi Home.">Raspberry Pi</a> is a small microcomputer that teaches computer science techniques to people of all ages.</p>

<!--more-->

<figure class="l-page">
  <img src="/images/projects/rpi/rpi_1.JPG" alt="Raspberry Pi Case." />
  <figcaption>Now that's a case.</figcaption>
