<p>I primarily use my RPi to use Python and tinker with small automation projects, so my RPi typically sits on my desk. I machined this solid aluminum case to protect the RPi from harmful outside interaction. The design maintains the Raspberry Piâ€™s functionality by leaving the sides open and LEDâ€™s visible while also allowing for others to view the microcomputer. The case looks great on a desk too.</p>

